Introduction

NVee is an American singer and actress who works under DR Music. She is a member of the multinational girl group BLACKSWAN.

Her addition to the group was revealed on December 24, 2022, in a Christmas pictorial behind-the-scene before being officially introduced on the 26th through an interview on the group's official channel.
